<p>Really looking forward to reading more of this. I can tell that the character really came to life for you, because she really jumped off the page for me. In a setting where most characters simply fit a &quot;exposition delivery&quot; role, Alai really has potential to bring more of the human touch to the Foundationverse. Can't wait to see what you're going to do with her; a naive character with a (in-universe) plausible reason to be so is very exciting.</p>
<p>Cheers. Easiest upvote in a while.</p>

							</div>

								
					
